### ========================================
### INTER ISMAEL - TEST ENDPOINTS
### ========================================
### Backend runs on http://localhost:3333
### Run with: npm run dev (in app/backend)
### Worker runs parallel: npm run dev (in app/worker)

### ========================================
### 1. ESCANEO (POST /scan)
### ========================================

### ✅ Escanear guía nueva - LOCAL
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "deliveryType": "LOCAL",
  "zoneId": 1,
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ✅ Escanear guía - Entrega ZONA
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "9876543210",
  "deliveryType": "ZONA",
  "zoneId": 5,
  "scannedBy": "Juan"
}

### ✅ Rescannear guía existente (UPDATE)
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "deliveryType": "LOCAL",
  "zoneId": 2,
  "scannedBy": "Maria"
}

### ❌ Error - tracking muy corto
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "123",
  "deliveryType": "LOCAL",
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ❌ Error - deliveryType inválido
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "1111111111",
  "deliveryType": "EXPRESS",
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ❌ Error - zoneId no existe
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "2222222222",
  "deliveryType": "ZONA",
  "zoneId": 999,
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ========================================
### 2. MONITOREO DE GUÍAS (Shipments)
### ========================================

### Listar todas las guías
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments

### Ver guía específica
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/1234567890

### Ver jobs de una guía
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/1234567890/jobs

### Exportar a CSV
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export

### Exportar con filtros
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export?status=INGRESADA&zoneId=1

### ========================================
### 3. GESTIÓN DE ZONAS
### ========================================

### Listar zonas activas
GET http://localhost:3333/zones?active=1

### Listar todas las zonas
GET http://localhost:3333/zones

### Ver zona específica
GET http://localhost:3333/zones/1

### Crear nueva zona
POST http://localhost:3333/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Centro"
}

### Crear zona 2
POST http://localhost:3333/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Norte"
}

### Actualizar zona (nombre + active flag)
PATCH http://localhost:3333/zones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Centro - Actualizada",
  "active": true
}

### Desactivar zona
PATCH http://localhost:3333/zones/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}

### ========================================
### 4. MONITOREO DE JOBS
### ========================================

### Listar todos los jobs
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs

### Listar jobs PENDING
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=PENDING

### Listar jobs FETCH_PAYMENT_API
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?type=FETCH_PAYMENT_API

### Listar jobs WAITING_NET (retries)
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=WAITING_NET

### Ver resumen de jobs (estadísticas)
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/summary

### Ver job específico
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/1

### Buscar jobs por tracking number
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?q=1234567890

### Listar con paginación
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?limit=20&offset=0

### Ver todos los jobs de una guía
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/tracking/1234567890

### ========================================
### FLUJO COMPLETO DE PRUEBA
### ========================================

### Paso 1: Crear zona
POST http://localhost:3333/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Test"
}

### Paso 2: Escanear guía (crea FETCH_PAYMENT_API job automáticamente)
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "5555555555",
  "deliveryType": "ZONA",
  "zoneId": 1,
  "scannedBy": "Tester"
}

### Paso 3: Ver jobs pendientes
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=PENDING

### Paso 4: Esperar 5 segundos (worker poll) → Worker ejecuta FETCH_PAYMENT_API
### Ver logs en terminal del worker

### Paso 5: Ver resumen actualizado
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/summary

### Paso 6: Ver datos de guía actualizados
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/5555555555


{
  "trackingNumber": "123456789",
  "deliveryType": "LOCAL",
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ❌ Error - trackingNumber con letras
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "ABC1234567",
  "deliveryType": "LOCAL",
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ❌ Error - deliveryType inválido
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "deliveryType": "EXPRESS",
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ❌ Error - zoneId negativo
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "deliveryType": "ZONA",
  "zoneId": -1,
  "scannedBy": "Admin"
}

### ❌ Error - scannedBy vacío
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "deliveryType": "LOCAL",
  "scannedBy": ""
}

### ❌ Error - officeStatus inválido
POST http://localhost:3333/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "deliveryType": "LOCAL",
  "scannedBy": "Admin",
  "officeStatus": "ESTADO_INEXISTENTE"
}

### ✅ Listar todas las guías
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments

### ✅ Obtener guía específica
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/1234567890

### ✅ Ver jobs de una guía
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/1234567890/jobs

### ✅ Ver guías con jobs pendientes
GET http://localhost:3333/scan/pending
### ========== ZONES CRUD ==========

### ✅ Listar todas las zonas
GET http://localhost:3333/zones

### ✅ Listar solo zonas activas
GET http://localhost:3333/zones?active=1

### ✅ Listar solo zonas inactivas
GET http://localhost:3333/zones?active=0

### ✅ Crear zona
POST http://localhost:3333/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Centro Histórico"
}

### ✅ Crear otra zona
POST http://localhost:3333/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Industrial"
}

### ✅ Obtener zona específica (id=1)
GET http://localhost:3333/zones/1

### ✅ Actualizar zona - cambiar nombre
PATCH http://localhost:3333/zones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Centro"
}

### ✅ Actualizar zona - desactivar
PATCH http://localhost:3333/zones/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}

### ✅ Actualizar zona - nombre y activo
PATCH http://localhost:3333/zones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zona Central",
  "active": true
}

### ❌ Error - nombre vacío
POST http://localhost:3333/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### ❌ Error - zona duplicada
POST http://localhost:3333/zones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Centro Histórico"
}

### ❌ Error - zona no existe
GET http://localhost:3333/zones/9999

### ❌ Error - ID inválido
GET http://localhost:3333/zones/abc

### ❌ Error - PATCH sin campos
PATCH http://localhost:3333/zones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### ❌ Error - PATCH nombre vacío
PATCH http://localhost:3333/zones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "   "
}

### ========== EXPORT CSV ==========

### ✅ Exportar todas las guías a CSV
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export

### ✅ Exportar filtrando por estado
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export?status=PAQUETE_INGRESADO

### ✅ Exportar filtrando por tipo de entrega
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export?deliveryType=LOCAL

### ✅ Exportar filtrando por zona
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export?zoneId=1

### ✅ Exportar por rango de fechas
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export?from=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2025-12-31T23:59:59Z

### ✅ Exportar combinando múltiples filtros
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export?status=PAQUETE_CARGADO&deliveryType=ZONA&zoneId=5

### ✅ Exportar por intervalo de fechas (reciente)
GET http://localhost:3333/shipments/export?from=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z

### ========== JOBS MONITORING ==========

### ✅ Listar todos los jobs
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs

### ✅ Listar jobs con paginación
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?limit=50&offset=0

### ✅ Filtrar jobs por status
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=PENDING

### ✅ Filtrar jobs por status DONE
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=DONE

### ✅ Filtrar jobs por status FAILED
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=FAILED

### ✅ Filtrar jobs por status WAITING_NET
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=WAITING_NET

### ✅ Filtrar jobs por type
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?type=FETCH_PAYMENT_API

### ✅ Filtrar jobs por type FETCH_PORTAL_APX
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?type=FETCH_PORTAL_APX

### ✅ Buscar jobs por tracking_number (like)
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?q=1234567890

### ✅ Búsqueda parcial de tracking
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?q=123456

### ✅ Combinar filtros: status + type
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=PENDING&type=FETCH_PAYMENT_API

### ✅ Combinar filtros: status + búsqueda
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs?status=FAILED&q=987654

### ✅ Resumen de jobs por status y type
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/summary

### ✅ Obtener un job específico por ID
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/1

### ✅ Obtener todos los jobs de un tracking_number
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/tracking/1234567890

### ❌ Error - Job ID inválido
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/abc

### ❌ Error - Job no existe
GET http://localhost:3333/jobs/9999
